{"title":"Donate to Win This Year’s Paul Comp Wild Sierra Roamer by HotSalad Bicycles","link":"https://bikerumor.com/donate-to-win-paul-comp-wild-sierra-roamer-by-hotsalad-bicycles/","date":1713276000000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-hero.jpeg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photo/Paul Component)\" /></p>\n<p>It’s that time of year again, the Sea Otter Classic is upon us. For many, it’s not only an exciting time to get together and celebrate the bicycle, but it’s also an exciting time to see what Paul Components brewed up for <a href=\"https://sierranevada.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sierra Nevada Brewing</a> and the annual custom, one-off bike offering. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-anodizing.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-anodizing.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike custom anodizing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-anodizing.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-anodizing-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-anodizing-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-anodizing-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-anodizing-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-anodizing-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Paul Components)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For the 7th year in a row, Sierra Nevada Brewery has asked Paul Components to bring a custom bike to the Sea Otter. They then give away this bike to raise money for a non-profit. And these bikes are like no other bike at the show, or that you’ve ever seen. Each year brings a bicycle with a high level of customization, creativity, and uniqueness.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p>And this year’s bike offering is no different!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Celebrate and Elevate Diversity in Mountain Biking</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>“<em>This year we wanted to help create a space at Sea Otter to focus on all the badass women in the cycling scene, and Sierra Nevada said, “YES, let’s do that!” So we’ve partnered up with <a href=\"https://www.theroamcollective.org/\" target=\"_blank\">The Roam Collective</a>, who will be doing a takeover at the Sierra Nevada Beer Garden during the event. They’ll be hosting some rad inclusivity panels, Shredtalks, and meetups. Then, we’ll be giving this bike away to a lucky winner as a way to raise money and awareness for Roam</em>“. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Refusing to bring a boring bike to Sea Otter, Paul Components continues to not disappoint with this collaboration. It’s a beautifully weird and wonderful, curvy titanium frame made by B Vivit of <a href=\"https://hotsaladbicycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">HotSalad Bicycles</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hotsalad-Cycles-B-Vivit-jpeg.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hotsalad-Cycles-B-Vivit-jpeg.jpeg\" alt=\"Hotsalad-Cycles-B-Vivit-jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hotsalad-Cycles-B-Vivit-jpeg.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hotsalad-Cycles-B-Vivit-jpeg-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hotsalad-Cycles-B-Vivit-jpeg-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hotsalad-Cycles-B-Vivit-jpeg-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hotsalad-Cycles-B-Vivit-jpeg-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Hotsalad-Cycles-B-Vivit-jpeg-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>B Vivit of HotSalad Bicycles (Photo/Ron Frazelle)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You might remember when I mentioned B and HotSalad Bicycles in my coverage of the 2022 Philly Bike Expo. B was the winner of the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/philly-bike-expo-bikes-of-the-show/\">Philly Bike Expo/SRAM Inclusivity Scholarship</a>. And it was at the Expo where she displayed a very creative take on a titanium Klunker. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/jacquie-phelan-and-ottoLarge.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"912\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/jacquie-phelan-and-ottoLarge.jpeg\" alt=\"jacquie phelan and ottoLarge\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/jacquie-phelan-and-ottoLarge.jpeg 912w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/jacquie-phelan-and-ottoLarge-214x300.jpeg 214w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/jacquie-phelan-and-ottoLarge-86x120.jpeg 86w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/jacquie-phelan-and-ottoLarge-768x1078.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Jacquie Phelan and her bike, Otto. (Photo/Bike Recyclery)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike that she built for this year’s Paul/Sierra bike is a modern tribute to “<em>mountain biking’s original dirt crusher and advocate for women in cycling, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacquie_Phelan\" target=\"_blank\">Jacquie Phelan</a>, and her historic bike, “Otto”</em>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>This Year’s Bike</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-Vivit-of-HotSalad-Bicycles.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-Vivit-of-HotSalad-Bicycles.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike B Vivit of HotSalad Bicycles\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-Vivit-of-HotSalad-Bicycles.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-Vivit-of-HotSalad-Bicycles-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-Vivit-of-HotSalad-Bicycles-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-Vivit-of-HotSalad-Bicycles-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-Vivit-of-HotSalad-Bicycles-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-Vivit-of-HotSalad-Bicycles-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>B Vivit at work</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This bike looks pretty amazing. It’s a cool blend of old-school and new, cutting-edge technology. It’s not only a custom titanium frame, but it’s decked out with a SRAM Electronic Transmission, drop bars, cloth handlebar tape, and a vintage Hite-Rite saddle dropper. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-with-the-front-triangle.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"853\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-with-the-front-triangle.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike B with the front triangle\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-with-the-front-triangle.jpeg 853w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-with-the-front-triangle-200x300.jpeg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-with-the-front-triangle-80x120.jpeg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-with-the-front-triangle-768x1152.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-welding-bottom-bracket.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"853\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-welding-bottom-bracket.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike B welding bottom bracket\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-welding-bottom-bracket.jpeg 853w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-welding-bottom-bracket-200x300.jpeg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-welding-bottom-bracket-80x120.jpeg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-B-welding-bottom-bracket-768x1152.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The real hero of the bike set-up is the swoopy and curvy titanium frame with gorgeous, custom anodizing that B put together. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Ti-LD-stem.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Ti-LD-stem.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike Ti LD stem\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Ti-LD-stem.jpeg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Ti-LD-stem-240x300.jpeg 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Ti-LD-stem-96x120.jpeg 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Ti-LD-stem-768x960.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And yes, the LD stem is a custom titanium version, bringing the finishing touch to the tribute to Otto. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Jen-Green-HeadBadge-e1713216146366.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"985\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Jen-Green-HeadBadge-e1713216146366.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike Jen Green HeadBadge\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Jen-Green-HeadBadge-e1713216146366.jpeg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Jen-Green-HeadBadge-e1713216146366-297x286.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Jen-Green-HeadBadge-e1713216146366-120x115.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Jen-Green-HeadBadge-e1713216146366-768x739.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Jen Green Head Badge</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Jen Green made the beautiful handmade headtube badge for this bike using copper, brass, and nickel. It looks amazing. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Sim-Works-bars.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Sim-Works-bars.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike Sim Works bars\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Sim-Works-bars.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Sim-Works-bars-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Sim-Works-bars-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Sim-Works-bars-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Sim-Works-bars-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Sim-Works-bars-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Sim Works handlebars</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-SRAM-Transmission.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-SRAM-Transmission.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike SRAM Transmission\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-SRAM-Transmission.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-SRAM-Transmission-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-SRAM-Transmission-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-SRAM-Transmission-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-SRAM-Transmission-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-SRAM-Transmission-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>SRAM Transmission </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-cloth-tape.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-cloth-tape.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike custom cloth tape\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-cloth-tape.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-cloth-tape-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-cloth-tape-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-cloth-tape-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-cloth-tape-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-custom-cloth-tape-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Custom cloth bar tape</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Ind-cranks.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Ind-cranks.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike White Ind cranks\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Ind-cranks.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Ind-cranks-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Ind-cranks-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Ind-cranks-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Ind-cranks-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Ind-cranks-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>White Ind. Cranks</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike also sports donations for some top-end bike part makers, like White Industries, Paul Components, Velocity USA, Simworks, Ultradynamico, King Cage, Forager Cycles, and WTB. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-paul-Klamper.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-paul-Klamper.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike paul Klamper\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-paul-Klamper.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-paul-Klamper-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-paul-Klamper-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-paul-Klamper-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-paul-Klamper-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-paul-Klamper-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-crazy-details.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-crazy-details.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike crazy details\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-crazy-details.jpeg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-crazy-details-240x300.jpeg 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-crazy-details-96x120.jpeg 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-crazy-details-768x960.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Industries-rear-hub.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Industries-rear-hub.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike White Industries rear hub\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Industries-rear-hub.jpeg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Industries-rear-hub-240x300.jpeg 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Industries-rear-hub-96x120.jpeg 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-White-Industries-rear-hub-768x960.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Vintage-Hite-Rite.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Vintage-Hite-Rite.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike Vintage Hite-Rite\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Vintage-Hite-Rite.jpeg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Vintage-Hite-Rite-240x300.jpeg 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Vintage-Hite-Rite-96x120.jpeg 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Vintage-Hite-Rite-768x960.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Let’s Meet the Collaborators</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li> Titanium Frame and Stem by <a href=\"https://hotsaladbicycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">HotSalad Bicycles</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Brakes, Seatpost. and Seatcollar by <a href=\"https://www.paulcomp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">PAUL Component</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Cranks, Chainring, Bottom Bracket, Headset, and Hubs by <a href=\"https://www.whiteind.com/\" target=\"_blank\">White Industries</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rims by <a href=\"https://www.velocityusa.com/home/\" target=\"_blank\">Velocity USA</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Headtube Badge by <a href=\"https://www.headbadges.com/store/c1/headbadges\" target=\"_blank\">Jen Green</a>      </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Titanium Bottle Cages by <a href=\"https://kingcage.com/\" target=\"_blank\">King Cage</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Handlebar, Cablehousing, and Pedals by <a href=\"https://www.sim.works/\" target=\"_blank\">Simworks</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tires by <a href=\"https://ultradynamico.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Ultradynamico</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Gravelier Saddle and Tire Sealant by <a href=\"https://www.wtb.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WTB</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>R7 Pro Fork by <a href=\"https://hayesbicycle.com/products/r7pro_z\" target=\"_blank\">Manitou</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>12 Speed AXS Shifters, Derailleur, Chain, and Cassette by <a href=\"https://www.sram.com/en/sram\" target=\"_blank\">SRAM</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>CNC Cable Tips by <a href=\"https://foragercycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Forager Cycles</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li> “Dropper” by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hite_rite/\" target=\"_blank\">Hite-Rite</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Check ROAM Collective…</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This bike <em>should</em> get you motivated to make the trip to the Sea Otter Classic this year. If you are going to make it, check out <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/the.roam.collective/\" target=\"_blank\">ROAM Collective’s Instagram</a> account for the schedule for the panels that they will be hosting at the show. The Sierra Nevada beer garden is where they’ll be taking over. It’s also where you can find this bike to drool over in person.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you aren’t heading over to Sea Otter you can go to ROAM’s website anytime before May 16th, where every $5 you donate gets you an entry to win this beautifully unique, one-of-a-kind steed all while helping to make mountain biking a more diverse, inclusive, and fun culture for everybody. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Velocity-USA-and-Ultradynamico.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Velocity-USA-and-Ultradynamico.jpeg\" alt=\"Paul Comp Sierra Roamer Custom Bike Velocity USA and Ultradynamico\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Velocity-USA-and-Ultradynamico.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Velocity-USA-and-Ultradynamico-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Velocity-USA-and-Ultradynamico-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Velocity-USA-and-Ultradynamico-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Velocity-USA-and-Ultradynamico-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Paul-Comp-Sierra-Roamer-Custom-Bike-Velocity-USA-and-Ultradynamico-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Donate to Win <a href=\"https://www.theroamcollective.org/\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a>!</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>All of the component companies that contributed are linked in the above list, and check out the link below for more from the parent brands that brought you this year’s custom steed! </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.paulcomp.com/\">PaulComp.com</a></em></p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://hotsaladbicycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">HotSaladBicycles.com</a></em></p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.theroamcollective.org/\" target=\"_blank\">TheRoamCollective.com</a></em></p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://sierranevada.com/\" target=\"_blank\">SierraNevada.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/donate-to-win-paul-comp-wild-sierra-roamer-by-hotsalad-bicycles/\">Donate to Win This Year’s Paul Comp Wild Sierra Roamer by HotSalad Bicycles</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"7a04967fa1bf49faf3b47e05d2ed15113f775d400e175db8aa7f5888ad16cafe","category":"Cycling"}